cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.DB (Databases), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as these sub-categories are closely related to the field of data-driven discovery and the analysis of influential works in this field. The paper discusses the collection and analysis of references related to big data for scientific discovery, which is a topic that is relevant to all of these sub-categories.
